latestIgtvVideos.title: SMOKEY EYE TUTORIAL  bipasha_roy__  ep.2
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hello guys.. Here is my smokey eye tutorial. So we all know that smokey eyes looks are so gorgeous, so I just gave it a shot on how to do your smokey eyes with minimal products. Not everything is affordable, some products are pocket friendly and some are not as we all are aware of the situation. So I just made it with whatever I have now with me( I hope this situation gets better soon).
I hope you people like it.
*Bear with the poor lighting 😓*
If you like it, please please give it a like and share.
Keep following me 😚✌️
Following are the products that I used in my video- 
1. @ayur.herbals Ayur skin toner
2. @cetaphil_india Cetaphil moisturising cream
3. @neutrogena Neutrogena ultra sheer dry - touch  sunblock 
4- @laneigeindia Laneige lip sleeping mask ( Berry )
5- @flowerbeauty Flower beauty light illisuion concealer
6- @maybelline Maybelline Fit me foundation- 120
